  "prompt": "Will Arya kill Cersei?",
  "response": "In the television series \"Game of Thrones,\" Arya Stark does not kill Cersei Lannister. Cersei meets her end when the Red Keep collapses due to the wildfire explosion caused by Daenerys Targaryen's dragon, Drogon, during the battle for King's Landing. Arya and The Hound confront Cersei in the keep, but ultimately, Arya chooses not to go after Cersei and instead escapes the collapsing fortress.\n\nIn the books, \"A Song of Ice and Fire\" by George R.R. Martin, the story has not yet reached the same point as the TV series, so Cersei's fate remains uncertain in that narrative. It is unknown whether Arya will be the one to kill Cersei, if anyone does, in the books.",
